# Splunk JWT token for nike.splunkcloud.com
#
# Setup:
#   1. Go to https://nike.splunkcloud.com/en-US/app/initialize_nike/welcome_nike
#   2. Settings -> Tokens -> New Token -> Create
#   3. Copy the token (shown only once)
#   4. Run: cp .cursor/skills/ops-query-splunk/splunk_token.txt.example .cursor/skills/ops-query-splunk/splunk_token.txt
#   5. Replace everything in .cursor/skills/ops-query-splunk/splunk_token.txt with your raw token (no quotes, no trailing newline)
#
# Alternatively, export SPLUNK_JWT_TOKEN=<your-token> in your shell or place a shared fallback token at ~/.cursor/skills/ops-query-splunk/splunk_token.txt.
#
# splunk_token.txt is gitignored -- never commit a real token.
